data.eml:eml: A checklist of the amphibians and reptiles of Honduras, with additions, comments on taxonomy, some recent taxonomic decisions, and areas of further studies needed

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Mccranie, James R. (2015): A checklist of the amphibians and reptiles of Honduras, with additions, comments on taxonomy, some recent taxonomic decisions, and areas of further studies needed. Zootaxa 3931 (3): 352-386, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3931.3.2
